kudos Code Style
================

Indentation
  C: 2 spaces
  Assembly: tabs

Naming
  lower case
  underscores

Constants
  #define

Braces
  K&R

Spaces
  Around keywords apart from sizeof, typeof, alignof, and __attribute__
  * adjacent to data/function name
  Around binary/ternary operators (not unary)
  (Avoid trailing whitespace)
